<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by krintar:
[B]OK you came to Rallos Zek for the PvP. You came for 1 of 2 reasons. 1 you wanna get more of a sense of realism roleplaying where anything you do will affect another. Or 2 you just wanna go out and totaly torment others. This server is the ultimate! Yes there are a lot of downsides to this server. Biggest downside is that you will on a regular basis find your self getting murdered speacially when those hps get below 1/2. Yes it sucks, but it adds 1 more element to make this game even more exciteing. I am not much of a pker but like a lot of others i have my moments. If you are new to this server there are a few words of advice to go by. 1 is not to hunt in a populated newbie zone!! You will find yourself for hours dieing and going back to the spawn point only to find a new set of pkers right there by ya. 2 is when wounded, no matter how bad the inconvienice is,you locate a corner or any ground that conceals you from others. Hide out there till you regain your health. Trust me 9 out of every 10 of your deaths will be because someone will see you at low life and even a low leveler can take you out with relative ease. Once you make level 12 on this server you can start feeling a bit more secure about protecting yourself, but untill then follow the above tips. You follow these basic tips you will make your levels quick. Oh and one more tip. If you get pkes, write there name down. Wait a day or 2 till you level. Then when you feel you can take them send them a tell asking them if they wanna group or something. More then likely they will have no clue who you are and will maybe accept. Find them and givce them yor greetings =) Good luck all and enjoy[/B][/QUOTE]

</TEXTAREA>
